                   throws SAXException
        Discretizes a time series using N threads.
        Parameters:
        timeseries - the input time series.
        threadsNum - the number of threads to allocate for conversion.
        slidingWindowSize - the SAX sliding window size.
        paaSize - the SAX PAA size.
        alphabetSize - the SAX alphabet size.
        nrStrategy - the SAX numerosity reduction strategy.
        normalizationThreshold - the normalization threshold.
        Returns:
        a SAX representation of the input time series.
        Throws:
        SAXException - if error occurs.
